The calorimeter tower offset at the EM scale is derived by measuring the average tower transverse energy for all towers in events with NPV=1,2,…,N and comparing directly to events with \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
