				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$p^{\text{track jet}}_{\mathrm{T}}$\end{document} can establish the systematic uncertainty of the pile-up correction.

