				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$p_{\mathrm {T}} ^{\mathrm{jet}} > 30~ \mathrm{GeV} $\end{document}. In the endcap and forward regions, the closure is less than 1 % for \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
