				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$p^{\text{track jet}}_{\mathrm{T}}$\end{document}-bins. This estimation translates directly into a 20 % uncertainty on the jet-based offset. The resulting systematic uncertainty on jets corrected by the offset correction is estimated to be \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
