				\begin{document}$p_{\mathrm{T}} ^{\mathrm{jet}}$\end{document}, this choice leads to partially double counting the contribution from the dead material uncertainty, but it leads to a conservative estimate in a region where it is difficult to estimate the accuracy of the material description.

