				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$p_{\mathrm{T}} ^{\mathrm{jet}}$\end{document} resolution is 5 % for 0≤|η|<0.8 and 10 % for 0.8≤|η|<2.1. The effect of this variation is largest for low values of \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
