The double ratio of charged-to-total momentum observed in data to that obtained in Monte Carlo simulation defined in Eq. (23) will be referred to as \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
