				\begin{document}$R_{r_{\mathrm{trk}}, \mathrm{inclusive}}$\end{document}. In analogy this ratio is studied for b-tagged jets: 
62\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
