				\begin{document}$\sqrt{s}=7~ \mathrm{TeV} $\end{document} are reconstructed with the anti-kt algorithm with distance parameters R=0.4 or R=0.6. The energy and the direction of the jets are calibrated with simple factors derived from Monte Carlo simulations for transverse jet momenta \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
